    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389170/extras/aeca58fe810ffb995e072d838a1777d8.poster.avif?t=1772019017\" width=1170 height=792 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389170/extras/aeca58fe810ffb995e072d838a1777d8.webm?t=1772019017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389170/extras/aeca58fe810ffb995e072d838a1777d8.mp4?t=1772019017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">周威烈王二十有三年，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">韩、趙、魏三家分晋，是谓战国。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">此诚天地倾覆、神魔乱舞之秋。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">尔起于奴人之身，拔剑纵横直至问鼎中原。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389170/extras/7bacd9c5c42ff0e2f0a4f490aed1a7fc.poster.avif?t=1772019017\" width=1170 height=792 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389170/extras/7bacd9c5c42ff0e2f0a4f490aed1a7fc.webm?t=1772019017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389170/extras/7bacd9c5c42ff0e2f0a4f490aed1a7fc.mp4?t=1772019017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">聚门客、练死士、筑坚城、通商道，富国强兵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">是冲锋陷阵或排兵布阵，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">合纵连横或独霸天下，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">听汝号令。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389170/extras/38b08ae30fe480789f3c5c047affd43c.poster.avif?t=1772019017\" width=1170 height=792 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389170/extras/38b08ae30fe480789f3c5c047affd43c.webm?t=1772019017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389170/extras/38b08ae30fe480789f3c5c047affd43c.mp4?t=1772019017\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">治国之策，争霸之路，皆使君旨意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">是成帝王业，还是传万世名？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">战国之策，凭君写就！</p>",
